Sobral
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A227579FFFEF9D20FDB0FAAEF5E5FA9E" box="[556,651,1302,1328]" pageId="27" pageNumber="46" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
Type: 
